flowchart LR
    CTX[Repository, issue, policy, and retrieved context] --> MODEL[Model and prompt version]
    MODEL --> OUT[Suggestion, finding, patch, or plan]
    OUT --> HUMAN[Human validation and decision]
    HUMAN --> ART[Accepted artifact or rejection]
    ART --> RESULT[Build, deployment, quality, and operational outcome]

    META[Tokens, latency, cost, permissions, and tool calls] -. provenance .-> MODEL
    META -. provenance .-> OUT
    OUT -. linked to .-> EC[Engineering Change]
    RESULT -. feedback .-> EVAL[Evaluation and model monitoring]
